Class TnaSlTM

TrustAlg
public class TnaSlTM
extends java.lang.Object
implements TrustAlg

The TnaSlTM class conforms to the TrustAlg interface and implements the 'Trust Network Analysis with Subjective Logic' approach of Josang et. al.
